"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The code uses sns.set_context() to set the context parameters, but it is incorrectly using the rc argument to set parameters that are not part of the context definition. The parameters 'grid.linewidth' and 'grid.color' should be set using sns.set_style() instead, as they are related to figure aesthetics rather than context settings.\", \"patch\": \"9c9\\n< sns.set_context(rc=viz_dict)\\n---\\n> sns.set_style(rc=viz_dict)\"}"